properties.title: Whitney Museum
properties.description: The Whitney Museum of American Art, known informally as 'The Whitney', is an art museum in the Meatpacking District and West Village neighborhoods.

properties.title: Vessel
properties.description: Vessel is a structure and visitor attraction built as part of the Hudson Yards Redevelopment Project.

properties.title: Little Island
properties.description: Little Island is a new public park where all New Yorkers and visitors can experience nature and art in a unique urban oasis on the Hudson River.

properties.title: The Shed
properties.description: In the center of Hudson Yard, the Shed commissions, produces, and presents a wide range of activities in performing arts, visual arts, and pop culture.

properties.title: ARTECHOUSE NYC
properties.description: Futuristic space with a focus on using vivid, interactive technology to explore art & science.
